test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert -18 == -36
 +  where -18 = <built-in function prod>([-18])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (0 == 3)
 +  where 0 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x71c60a9de4c0>([-36])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x71c60a9de4c0> = [[1], [1, -36], [-36, 1], [-36, 1, -36], [1], [1, -36], ...].count
